{
  "stem": "25639.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was sent to the infirmary, supposedly to heal, by Dr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Josef Mengele.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Simply because I had a rash from-- from the heat, and the humidity, and the filth, the dust, of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I obviously reacted to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in order to make sure that it's not something contagious, he isolated me by sending me to an infirmary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It-- It was just a little shack that is not a hospital, where there was no medicine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was a Hungarian inmate doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We called her Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Gizzy.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A little bitty woman-- she came up to my shoulders, and she spoke Hungarian to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember we slept the same as in barracks, in three tiers-- three-tier bunks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after the-- I forget-- the second night, I think it was-- the second or third night-- I think the second night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, after the second night, Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Gizzy came to me and said, 'Go back to your mother.' I said, 'You're releasing me.' 'Yes, because tonight there will be a [?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Razia.' ?] 'What's a [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Razia?' ?] 'Well, tonight they're going to come and pick up everybody who is unable to go back to the barrack.' I said, 'Thank you, Dr.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Gizzy.' In the meantime, nothing was done here on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember just sitting on some warm-- some warm heater.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But it was miserable there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Everybody was crying and moaning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were hurting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I wasn't hurting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was perfectly healthy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was afraid I'll catch something among all these people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I-- it was dark, and I was afraid I'll get shot if I go back to the barrack by myself.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I hesitated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Gizzy called somebody and said, 'Take her to such and such place.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
